{"tid":2121454,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港府推大規模檢測 華昇日驗三萬樣本","createTime":"2020-07-23T10:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T15:31:44.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"1cf5a8f258727110ba3e98ed1ae190261c30cb4b","tid":2121454,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"港府推大規模檢測 華昇日驗三萬樣本<br />\n2020-07-23 08:08<br />\n<br />\n&quot;華昇診斷中心上周獲政府委聘進行大規模病毒檢測，其董事長胡定旭接受《星島日報》專訪表示，中心目前每日可檢測五千個樣本，下周可增至三萬個&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;華昇診斷中心沿用華大在內地的測試方式，利用咽拭子，以人手採集檢測者的喉嚨分泌物，與本港沿用的深喉唾液樣本做法不同。擔任華昇診斷中心董事長的前醫管局行政總裁胡定旭解釋，深喉唾液樣本採樣要求高，過程易出現假陰性，相反咽拭子可隨時採樣，可靠度更高，「華大的測試劑已取得美國、歐盟、日本及澳洲的認證，亦已獲世衞列入緊急清單，全世界一百八十多個國家都有使用，所以不需要擔心準確性不足。」&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1826632/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8E%A8%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E8%8F%AF%E6%98%87%E6%97%A5%E9%A9%97%E4%B8%89%E8%90%AC%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1826632%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%2598%2587%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%25A9%2597%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E6%259C%25AC&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=1e4ad114\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1826632%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC-%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%2598%2587%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%25A9%2597%25E4%25B8%2589%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E6%259C%25AC&h=84b89b4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1826632/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BA%9C%E6%8E%A8%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC-%E8%8F%AF%E6%98%87%E6%97%A5%E9%A9%97%E4%B8%89%E8%90%AC%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">抗疫最終要靠華大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n(註: 據公司註冊處，華昇於上月9日成立，創辦成員包括萬隆福國際及華大基因健康科技（香港）有限公司，分別持六成及四成股份；後者登記地址位於大埔工業邨，由深圳華大基因股份有限公司全資持有。)"},{"pid":"3d3f2ed183c14daecfa6091fec36b9359ecc5ad6","tid":2121454,"uid":259088,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:11:14.000Z","msg":"比你永世做檢測有用？<br />\n<br />\n有元朗街坊見到大陸人一路行街一路播毒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2121428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2121428</a>"},{"pid":"a6f51efaa0fbc41253e66976b5f2e1c14236afb3","tid":2121454,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d3f2ed183c14daecfa6091fec36b9359ecc5ad6","tid":2121454,"uid":259088,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:11:14.000Z","msg":"比你永世做檢測有用？<br />\n<br />\n有元朗街坊見到大陸人一路行街一路播毒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2121428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2121428</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:40:06.000Z","msg":"好過無囉"},{"pid":"2c76529e4ac3854f7fcc967b8dd6264abdc899b0","tid":2121454,"uid":63782,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"美國制裁完華大基因<br />\n香港就用華大基因做檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b3a1a1f3d70795842c92575442753dec99621f","tid":2121454,"uid":183758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T11:26:45.000Z","msg":"DNA<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ed8d57de3c1362326278569b044c2ad28c9497","tid":2121454,"uid":50719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T11:29:53.000Z","msg":"基因圖譜奪取戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續恐懼啦～中央一定會打救香港人既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25d5e41a22b3913098aedc5bcafe5c017bbd4d0","tid":2121454,"uid":66087,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2c76529e4ac3854f7fcc967b8dd6264abdc899b0","tid":2121454,"uid":63782,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"美國制裁完華大基因<br />\n香港就用華大基因做檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T11:30:50.000Z","msg":"香港政府近幾年開始完全依賴大陸科技<br />\n<br />\n可能諗就算中美封關都冇問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae861cbebcb5b7d3adfc01953a78aced5bfcb08","tid":2121454,"uid":47614,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T11:30:58.000Z","msg":"另一間Prenetics 做檢測嘅係旗下Circle DNA<br />\n<br />\nCircle DNA由貝瑞基因和Prenetics共同投資創立<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">貝瑞基因是中國知名的臨床基因組學檢測公司</span>，成立於2010年，於2017年以A股上市，市值約20億美元。Prenetics公司成立於2014年，是由香港城市大學的科研中心分拆出來。總部設在香港，目前是東南亞和歐洲知名的基因檢測公司。<br />\n<br />\n技術源自於貝瑞基因<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><br />\nCircle DNA圓基因採用貝瑞基因的&rdquo;WES全外顯子組測序技術&rdquo;。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\">即刻兩間都係同中共有關</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8bba889842aef5211f1312a1bc71fc391c84ce","tid":2121454,"uid":60977,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T11:32:02.000Z","msg":"基因出賣俾國企"},{"pid":"4e42b309322c7fef4c55f0d5101e477678aa38cd","tid":2121454,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c76529e4ac3854f7fcc967b8dd6264abdc899b0","tid":2121454,"uid":63782,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"美國制裁完華大基因<br />\n香港就用華大基因做檢測<img src=\"/assets/faces/no